This is the code to generate text with AI


1. Choose models from this list:

For complex tasks choose one from this list:
 ["anthropic:claude-3-5-sonnet-latest" , "openai:gpt-4o"]

For less complex tasks choose one from this list:
["openai:gpt-4o-mini", "openai:gpt-4-turbo", "anthropic:claude-3-5-haiku-20241022"]

2. Create the PROMPT based on the input of the user, be explicit and verbose, pass verbatim if needed

3. Call the api/generate
Example:
        const response = await fetch("https://webdraw.com/api/generate?task=text", {
          method: "POST",
          body: JSON.stringify({
            model: "openai:gpt-4o-mini",
            messages: [{
                    role: "user",
                    content: "PROMPT HERE"
                  }]);

          }),
        });

Messages must be an array of jsons with role and content use "user"

If case you have a ton of voice of specific rules add system like this:

        const response = await fetch("https://webdraw.com/api/generate?task=text", {
          method: "POST",
          body: JSON.stringify({
            model: "openai:gpt-4o-mini",
            system: "SPECIFIC RULES OR TON OF VOICE"
            messages: [{
                    role: "user",
                    content: "PROMPT HERE"
                  }]);

          }),
        });


3. Retrieve the response
        const data = await response.json()

4. Use the text

        data.text

5. If the output contains markdowns you should render properly using corresponding html tags and styles

